#' @title Convert infiltration time columns to seconds
#'
#' @description For soil data, converts character strings displaying infiltration times in the format "HH:MM:SS" to seconds, returned as a numeric
#'
#' @param data
#' @param timeformat
#' @param inf_diameter
#' @param bd_diameter
#' @param volume
#' @param bd_height
#'
#'
#' @return data frame with added columns
#'
#' @examples data = add_datetime(data, timeformat = "yyyy-mm-dd")
#' @examples x = include_datetime(soildata, timeformat = "mm/dd/yyyy")
#'
#' @export add_soilcolumns
#'
#'
# Some useful keyboard shortcuts for package authoring:
#
#   Build and Reload Package:  'Ctrl + Shift + B'
#   Check Package:             'Ctrl + Shift + E'
#   Test Package:              'Ctrl + Shift + T'


